verbose_text: Moreover, the anti-drug antibody positive, but not the negative patients, showed significant increased levels of interferon-alpha (from 248.7 +/- 102.3 to 466.8 +/- 135.1 pg/mL, p = 0.0353) and B-cell activating factor (from 1073 +/- 75.1 to 1387 +/- 136.5 pg/mL, p = 0.0208) following infliximab treatment.
